            {
              "content": "=You are an AI news curator. Below are today's AI news articles. Create a concise daily digest that is suitable for a telegram message:\nToday's date is: {{ $now.setZone('Europe/London').toFormat('cccc d MMMM yyyy') }}\n\n- A brief 2-sentence overview of today's top theme\n- Each article summarized in 1-2 sentences with the title as a clickable link\n- Group by theme if possible (e.g. \"Model Releases\", \"Industry\", \"Research\")\n- Skip duplicate stories that appear from multiple sources\n- Make sure you only include articles that were posted in today {{ $now.setZone('Europe/London').toFormat('cccc d MMMM yyyy') }}. This is very important!! do not articles that were posted on any other day!!\n\n\n\nArticles:\n{{ $json.all_items }}\n"
            }
          ]
        },
